\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\ul\ulc0\sl480\slmult1\qc{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 Radiation}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\sl480\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab Upon the explosion of a nuclear bomb the solar force, once a part of a system, is now freed from it's system as stated in \'93Solar Force\'94.  There are many damaged atomic particles collected in the atmosphere left in chaos by the blast.  The main purpose of 
solar force is to continue it's cycle in order to maintain universal balance.  The damaged atoms are in a state of imbalance as their process has been stunned and is not in a properly balanced state.  The solar force and the damaged atoms are automatically
 attracted to each other, as they were originally joined before the blast, and together form a working system.  However, upon joining again, the damaged atoms are not fully capable of systemizing a solar cycle and in order for the solar force to continue i
t's cycle among the damaged atoms much friction evolves.  This friction dissipated rapidly as the solar force cycle repairs the atoms through magnetic uniting.  The friction that is present during the repairing of the atoms is known as radiation.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab An explosion is not necessary to create radiation.  It is only one source.  There are so many varied conditions that cause radiation that it would take a very detailed writing to go into them all, but radiation is always caused by some degree of imbalance
.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab As previously stated, the damaged atoms from a nuclear blast lack their natural magnetic inner support.  The solar force immediately begins to repair this through it's own magnetic uniting.  However, before the atom is completely restored much of the sola
r friction is allowed to enter the atmosphere, because of the atom's weakened magnetic state.  It is possible to create enough magnetism to support the system of each individual atom to allow them to pass the solar force from one to another, without causin
g any solar friction.  Before this could be accomplished, it would be necessary to contain the radiation to one area in order to concentrate that area with magnetism.  This could be done by creating a magnetic field encircling the area.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\ul\ulc0\sl480\slmult1\qc{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 Exploring the Theory on the Expanding Universe}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\sl480\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab It has been stated by scientists that all galaxies are moving away from each other,the fartherest  ones going the fastest.  That is as it is stated.  Now, let us delve into this theory.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab All galaxies travel at a left angle from their magnetic poles.  This is brought about through the law of balance that exists throughout the universe in all planes.  As galaxies increase in density through rotation of matter, or pure energy, the balance of
 their mass in the space that contains them would eventually become imbalanced.  In order to maintain that law of balance the universe requires the mass tilts it energy at a left angle to relieve the increased strain on it's poles and thus balance it's pos
ition in the universe.  The left angle tilt is due to all galaxies containing equalized pressure within themselves, making all tilts or shifts the same.  This slight angle would not be noticeable unless a galaxy was charted through space billions and billi
ons of light years.  The galaxy when first charted, in comparison to the same galaxy position after those many billions of light years, would reveal the slight left angle shift.  This system maintains the balance of the universe.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab The appearance of greater speed, the farther away the galaxy is form us, is due to the fact that as we view the galaxies from this earth plane, the fartherest ones in our vision are reaching the limitations of the earth plane.  This is stated in \'93The Eart
h in Relation to Other Planes\'94, and \'93The Infinity of the Universe\'94.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab In reality there is no expansion of the universe, for all energy pushing out from itself must eventually push back into itself in accordance with the law of the planes.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\ul\ulc0\sl480\slmult1\qc{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 The Creation of the Universe and All Therein}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\sl480\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab The universe, with all it's planes, galaxies, solar systems, and all it's many other compositions, was born of the need, through energy, to express the magnificance of the thought.  Upon creating this energy the thought became the creator, and through thi
s channel was given by the creator all the power and the glory.  The universe is the total and sole expression of the almighty, created for the souls which are not his expression but part of the thought that is God.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab The universe and it's planes were created as one, and through the universe the energy brought about existence.  Existence contains within it law.  Law is the ruling hand of God and all in his law are like the fingers of his hand.  The four major laws of t
he universe are:  the law of balance, the law of the planes, the law of time, and the law of continued existence.  The law of balance, and the law of the planes have been previously explained.  The time plane is the joint in the flexibility of the universe
.  It is set apart from all other planes.  The law of time is that all energy, even in those planes not interceded by the time plane, is subject to the time plane when it changes from one plane to another.  The law of continued existence is that all must c
ontinue forever. }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab Galaxies and solar sytems \'96 Since in each plane there is a different reaction that brings about the creation of galaxies and solar systems, this writing will deal mainly with the cause and reaction that comes about on the earth plane.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab Energy on the earth plane contains heat.  There are two variations of heat \'96 cold and hot.  The division between cold and hot is a misconception since both are an expression of heat on opposite ends of the heat scale.  Energy is not consistant in it's vib
rations.  They vary in intensity and frequency.  When an inconsistency occurs in the enrgy through the heat vibrations, and if the pattern of the inconsistency is not in accordance with the four major lows of the universe, the energy must disunite the inco
nsistent energy from the whole, leaving it as waste in the void of space.  There are certain points in space that contain energy concentrations due to certain suctions and overlapping of planes.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\ul\ulc0\sl480\slmult1\qc{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 The Creation of the Universe and All Therein}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\sl480\slmult1\qc{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 (Continued)}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\sl480\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 On the earth plane, with the heat factor present, the concentrations contain both cold and hot heat vibrations that are drawn and accumulate in suctions.  These heat vibrations were originally part of a whole energy mass composed solely of either hot or co
ld heat energy.  When these concentrations are in complete balance of hot and cold heat energy they remain as invisible concentrations of energy.  These are termed by scientists as quasars.  However, if the balance is not maintained, and there concentrates
 more of one heat variation than another, the whole of the energy concentration shifts and the law of balance is once again in command.  The cycle of solar force is interrupted and an explosion takes place.  The energy in the state of concentration pushed 
out, but through the expelling of it's solar force it abruptly changes it's action and contracts, pushing in.  In the vacuum of space this is allowed to continue until a core is formed and many different concentrations take substance in the energy sea arou
nd the core.  In this manner galaxies are formed.  A galaxy is a system and all systems, in accordance with the law of continued existence, must specialize their mass.  Solar sytems are formed by the heat energy that now finds itself a system and having bo
undaries.  Energy must always expel force and as a galaxy the energy must create within itself in order to utilize it's expelled force.  Like creates like causing duplication in order to maintain balance.  A completely formed galaxy once again pushes it's 
force out as it is again in balance with the universe.  Even the smallest atom follow the law of duplication.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\ul\ulc0\sl480\slmult1\qc{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 Energy}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\sl480\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab Energy is the first existing condition that was caused by the creation.  Upon creation of the universe energy remained for many billions of years solely in what I will term as first state energy.  First state energy is pure and limited to no plane, existi
ng in all of them, passing freely from one to another.  It contains the most force of all the energy states, yet it is the least violent, as it contains no matter.  First state energy speeds through the space of the earth plane so rapidly that it is undete
cted by our scientists.  When the waste of this energy is disunited from the whole, and is drawn to a suction in space to become part of a quasar, it changes to second state energy.  Second state energy differs from first state energy in the following ways
:  (1)  In first state the energy is moving in constant travel through the planes of the universe.  In second state the energy is fixed and limited to fewer planes.  (2)  When traveling on the earth plane, first state energy contains heat energy, each whol
e energy consisting of either hot or cold heat energy.  In first state, energy travels in condensed groups of one variation or the other, never mixing.  Second state energy combines the hot and cold heat energy and depends upon the balance of these two var
iations in order to remain in a second state energy form.  Second state energy is also in a pure form, and contains no matter in itself, but attracts matter from the energy sea surrounding the pure energy quasar and certain gases mix in the pure energy.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 \tab Pulsars are in a second state energy form the same as quasars.  They differ in intensity.  The quasars contain more pure energy force.  A pulsar is a small, extremely compact discarded energy once a part of a quasar.  It is not held by space suction and c
ollects more matter than a quasar because of it's slowly contracting magnetic field.  Pulsars are released from a quasar when a quasar is nearing an explosion due to universal imbalance.  In a vain attempt to maintain the law of balance the quasar disunite
s concentrated points of magnetism from it's shole which are thrown into space as pulsars.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\ul\ulc0\sl480\slmult1\qc{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 Energy}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\sl480\slmult1\qc{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\f0\fs24\lang4105\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang4105\i0\b0 (Continued)}
