aneling to be sensitive to first state energy.  By the command of the human mind the sensors will accept the flow of first state energy and the material of the paneling will undergo a chemical reaction that causes it to brighten when touched by the flow.  
In this way the beautiful, soft, non-radioactive light of first state energy can be seen.  In actuality the panels do not brighten but the chemical reaction that occurs causes them to be sensitive to the light essence of the energy and therefore the panels
