e spacecraft are able to enter through energy transference; but there is one device that must open to the surface.  This is a radar type object used in studying different energies of the earth plane.  It is usually oval in shape (this will differ) and is u
sually the size of a medium sized living room.  It is composed of a pattern of different energy cells sealed within a type of light defractor.  This object is placed only a few feet under the ground.  From the center of it stems a small elongated device th
at might resemble an antenna.  Only this is visible above the ground for from one half to two inches, depending on certain prevading conditions.  It appears to be white when seen at a distance but when approaching it it seems }
