t is automatically brought about by time.  Consequently, where a time factor is present, speed and distance are present.  As state in \'93Space\'94, space is the product of the holding conditions of time plus speed plus distance, thus space is a dimensional stro
nghold of values as a result of it's necessity for existence.  The determining of values unknown by scientists today could be acheived in a much closer examination of space.  }
